    <div class="post-container" id="fpc-4045372">
                      
		<div class="post" id="post-4045372">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,4045372)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-4045372">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205747" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;" >Weryllium</a></span> <span class="odate time_1540969412 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">31 Oct 2018 07:03</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4045372">
									

<p>I don't know how you did it <em>again</em>.</p>
<p>An entire goshdarned series, with characters that actually feel different from one another, a great plot and monster, all in such a short time frame. You absolute madman.</p>
<p>The use of narrative throughout this entire thing delicately balanced cleverness and plot without ever feeling in-your-face. It's no small feat for a tale to</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">spoilers&nbsp;i&nbsp;guess</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>fucking <strong>tell</strong> me a deus ex machina is coming, and still make that work</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>but you pulled even that off.</p>
<p>Bravo, Plastic Person. <em><strong>Bravo</strong></em>.</p>
<p>Can't wait for next Halloween!</p>

							</div>

								
					
